snippet.title: Super Metroid CRE 3 [SNES] Rom Hack
snippet.description:
Hack Created by Tundain
v1.0 https://metroidconstruction.com/hack.php?id=736
Release date: May 24, 2023

🆂🆄🅱🆂🅲🆁🅸🅱🅴 to my other channel:
https://youtube.com/@DoujinGamesPlay

"It's finally time for the completion of the CRE trilogy!
Samus ends up inside of the CRE tileset, filled with janky art, for the final time. Now with custom stuff! Also with custom music made by Tundain!"

Samus Graphics Redesign by Physix
